    "storage": "Store at \u221220\u00b0C for long-term, or 4\u00b0C for up to 4 weeks. Aliquot before first freeze to avoid repeated freeze-thaw. 50% glycerol storage buffer prevents freezing at \u221220\u00b0C.",
